name: Sir Erwin
message: So you are back? The guards should not let pass people like you

name: Traveler
message: Im here to see lady Liana

name: Sir Erwin
message: Are you? Lady Liana is a beggar lover, Im surprised she is still part of the royal family

name: Traveler
message: I dont care what you think, I just want to see her

name: Sir Erwin
message: Then go with here, I dont have time for you

name: Sir Erwin
message: Why are you still bothering me? little minion...
